views.text: The Secret Life of Amy Bensen
views.desc: The Secret Life of Amy Bensen

views.text: On a plane, struggling to face the devastation of losing everything again and starting over, Amy meets Liam Stone.
Liam escorts Amy to her apartment, where they get to know each other better.
Amy meets some new people and learns more about the life she’s been instructed to build in Denver, all while getting closer to Liam.
Amy and Liam grow closer as he opens up more about his life. Amy experiences a traumatic flashback, causing her to blackout. Liam tries to gain Amy’s trust.
Liam meets Jared when he stops by Amy’s apartment. Amy begins opening up to Liam. Liam grows more suspicious of Amy’s boss.

On the season finale, Liam has to travel to New York unexpectedly. Amy experiences a flashback, taking her back to the night she lost her family, injuring herself during the episode. Amy is shocked by something she overhears.
